{
  "stem": "12402.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left the whole store in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My kid brother registered as a German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He spoke good German-- they used to take the German-- they took the German back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They evacuated them from the East.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the Russian didn't want them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They shipped them back to-- to-- to the West, you know, German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he went with the-- the transports, my kid brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I lost him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he ended up in Cologne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then afterwards, he came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we run away middle of the night-- left the store there-- and we crossed the border, the Czech border, middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we went through all Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we got into-- went into Vienna, and stayed a-- a-- a month, maybe, in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we went-- I ended up in Munich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And from Munich, I heard there was a-- a place in Stuttgart-- there was 1,500 Jews, made a camp there, [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] ?] camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I went there, but I didn't stay and camp with the-- with the 1,500.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also, they shot maybe-- yeah, two Jews got shot in that camp, you know, from the German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I-- I took a place, private.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In order-- at that-- at that time, they give you-- for German-- if any Jew wanted to have quarters, they forced them to take you in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they gave me a room with a German family and I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and afterwards, I-- I didn't know-- I lost my brother again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I found out he-- he was in a camp not far from-- from Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Stuttgart, I met that-- met that girl-- she was-- she survived in Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
